# Notion integration for the `5 Notion` panel (read-only).
#
# 1. Create an internal integration at https://www.notion.so/my-integrations
#    with only the "Read content" capability.
# 2. Share your tickets page with that integration.
# 3. Copy the token below and export it in your shell (cawd reads the process
#    environment; it does not load this file automatically).
#
#   export NOTION_TOKEN=ntn_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

NOTION_TOKEN=

# Optional: override the source cawd reads tickets from. Accepts a raw page or
# database id, or a full Notion URL. Defaults to the "TASK RUN TECH" database.
# Note: the id must be shared with the integration above (otherwise Notion
# returns 404).
# NOTION_PAGE_ID=https://www.notion.so/3813b9213ea780c7b718fb7681d0904e

# Optional: name of the people property to treat as the assignee for the
# "assigned only" filter. Auto-detected by default (prefers lead/owner/assignee
# style names, e.g. "Tech lead"); set this to force a specific one.
# NOTION_ASSIGNEE_PROP=Tech lead
